on, edit PLAN_A.md for concision: remove duplication, tighten language, make it easier to scan.\n\nCommit and land PLAN_A.md per the workflow in AGENTS.md (agent-land.sh).\n","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","assignee":"Claude","owner":"noreply@anthropic.com","created_at":"2026-04-08T06:36:57Z","created_by":"Claude","updated_at":"2026-04-08T16:33:05Z","closed_at":"2026-04-08T14:58:44Z","close_reason":"Closed","dependency_count":0,"dependent_count":1,"comment_count":0}
